name: Complete
description:
Complete
Complete is an online co-op survival game where we kill the robots that attack us.

Characters
There are currently 2 different characters in the game and each character has their own unique abilities.

Robots
Robots are divided into two: close combat and marksman. As you level up, the damage and movement speed of the robots increases.

Items
You can gain features such as shield, movement speed and damage increase by using different items in the game.
